column5: Not 1,,,,not 2,,,,not 3,,,,but 4,,,Yes 4 Verado 275's It's also a cool pic  I say holy molly  - get in, sit down, shut up and hold on - of before we begin anyone care to split the gas This my new desktop    Cheers, Gman
easy way to clean your sinuses
Great picture.  How much will Bass Pro charge for shipping and duty to Ontario?
Looks like overkill to me, how fast do they really need to go???    Mike
WOW!  I wonder what the top end speed is...  I can't imagine they would get very far on a tank of gas with those 4 big boys on the back LOL!
Are they tied into that boat?
Well, that would be a fun ride, probably better than any roller coaster. AS for paying for a portion of gas, sure no problem, just as long as there is 45 people in the boat with me.
Wow what a ride that woud be!
wow,very nice could you imagine how much gas that machine will eat in 1 day?????
They are only trolling right now wait until they open it up.  Sam
That rig would be a b*tch to backtroll!
That is an outright waste of a resource, regardless if you have the money to blow on it.
with weather like that on the horizon give me as many motors as the boat can hold!
I just want the boat.....  would be happy with just one of the moters...But man i bet that would be one hell of a ride......
you wouldnt want to crank the wheel too fast in that baby...
